**Summary:**
This documentation covers the Android-Kotlin SDK for Amplitude analytics, including installation via Gradle/Maven with package `com.amplitude:analytics-android`, configuration options like `flushQueueSize`/`flushIntervalMillis`, autocapture features for sessions/app lifecycles/screen views/deep links/element interactions, tracking methods (`track()`, `identify()`, `revenue()`), plugin system with enrichment/destination types, and advanced features like COPPA control, advertising ID/app set ID usage, location tracking, and offline mode with network connectivity checking.

